{"tid":1800653,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"當曱甴開始會full gear會係商場亂拉亂打，其實商場只係下一個戰場","createTime":"2019-12-28T04:39:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T05:01:17.000Z","uid":24178,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7b228302c1bfea0aab81d32fc858c5bf8abbe683","tid":1800653,"uid":24178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:39:23.000Z","msg":"和理shop 同當初無不反話去元朗行街有分別?<br />\n上個禮拜拉左300 人啊<br />\n唔好再呃自己話我地唔Blackbloc 扮下行商場就無事啦<br />\n由商場放曱甴入來standby 果一下<br />\n商場就係另一個戰場<br />\n如果我地繼續手無寸鐡咁和理shop 只會死傷更慘烈<br />\n<br />\n一係就諗對策 一係就唔好係商場開 <br />\n手足們真係要諗諗<br />\n<br />\n利申支持經濟攬炒但用手足既血直接換返來我覺得唔值得"},{"pid":"5544ad2135a16d24366baf642e7e33fdd874cc5a","tid":1800653,"uid":49018,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:50:37.000Z","msg":"重點係佢告得啲乜<br />\n喺私人地方暴動？"},{"pid":"dbda6d56526032119be388498e1079947a8dc92d","tid":1800653,"uid":45830,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:51:15.000Z","msg":"我就日日blackbloc cover前線<br />\n俾人拉，俾人打，俾藍絲白眼，俾便衣狗搞就預左"},{"pid":"bb85bbc6d8d7482affaa2727f99f4829e0e7b79d","tid":1800653,"uid":24178,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5544ad2135a16d24366baf642e7e33fdd874cc5a","tid":1800653,"uid":49018,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:50:37.000Z","msg":"重點係佢告得啲乜<br />\n喺私人地方暴動？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:52:50.000Z","msg":"同一個問題我哋大學又問過行街又問過去機場又問過<br />\n要告咩好似係任黑驚開"},{"pid":"0f0a0f24df68c4e857eba35496810a76818bf2c0","tid":1800653,"uid":331973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:55:33.000Z","msg":"黑警告你商場遊蕩罪，只行吾消費。"},{"pid":"5e409985285179f13a20a1ed16fdaaa4ff0392d7","tid":1800653,"uid":24178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbda6d56526032119be388498e1079947a8dc92d","tid":1800653,"uid":45830,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:51:15.000Z","msg":"我就日日blackbloc cover前線<br />\n俾人拉，俾人打，俾藍絲白眼，俾便衣狗搞就預左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTim